{{wikipedia|dab=secretary (disambiguation)|secretary}}
==English==

===Etymology===
From {{ML.}} ''[[secretarius]]'', one entrusted with [[secret]]s.

===Pronunciation===
/ˈsekrətəri/, /<tt>"sekr@t@ri</tt>/
* {{audio|en-us-secretary.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-noun|secretaries}}

# {{obsolete}} Someone entrusted with a [[secret]].
# A person who keeps [[records]], takes [[notes]] and handles general [[clerical]] work.
# The [[head]] of a [[department]] of [[government]].
# A managerial or leading position in certain non-profit organizations, such as political parties, trade unions, international organizations.
#: ''Ban Ki-Moon is the current secretary general of the United Nations.''
# A type of [[desk]].
# A species of [[bird]]; ''Sagittarius serpentarius''.

